而論<br />\n例如有阻止訴訟對方移走資產既禁制令<br />\n又有阻止他人發表誹謗言論既禁制令<br />\n官司未開始同開始咗既禁制令又唔同<br />\n單方面緊急申請既禁制令同對方獲得通知既申請要求亦唔同<br />\n<br />\n好籠統咁講，門檻係好高既<br />\n首先你要說服到法庭你有一個valid claim<br />\n然後你個claim必須係錢唔能夠解決既問題(damages must be inadequate)<br />\n同埋法庭要平衡出禁制令的利害(balance of convenience)，對申請人既利要大於對被告既害<br />\n<br />\n可以參考：<a href=\"http://www.hkclic.org/en/topics/civilCase/commencement_of_trial/q6.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkclic.org%2Fen%2Ftopics%2FcivilCase%2Fcommencement_of_trial%2Fq6.shtml&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=a4d4b051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkclic.org/en/topics/civilCase/commencement_of_trial/q6.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"15611c372e105eee990dcc22c83b4089f81abec0","tid":1508997,"uid":236957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:15:47.000Z","msg":"試答巴打問可唔可以禁止警察蒙頭<br />\n<br />\n要達到第一個門檻，即係有一個valid claim已經有難度<br />\n因為據我所知並無法例禁止警察唔show編號<br />\n同時申請者好難證明監警會係一個完全無用既解決機制<br />\n<br />\n就平衡利害黎講，法庭亦可能會擔心禁制令影響警方執法<br />\n<br />\n掟磚引玉，歡迎有識之士指正<br />\n禁佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc94e81ffaf15988fd88d9ecb34037301f0e21b7","tid":1508997,"uid":45466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f4336ccc35c61c841022bab7c77722ebc39931a","tid":1508997,"uid":215667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"其實禁制令有咩類別 <br />\n有冇咩野既申請程序 <br />\n有冇申請費用<br />\n需要咩理據先可以令法庭頒令<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以禁止警員蒙頭 <br />\n原因係警員不出示委任證 身上又有警員編號 <br />\n當濫權執法時 或不禮貌對待市民時 <br />\n市民完全冇投訴既資料同方法 <br />\n<br />\n求解答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464712-20190624.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464712-20190624.htm&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=56070e02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2